            <div type="apparatus">
                <ab>1. Aeolic or Doric for <w lemma="ἐξαίφνης">ἐξαίφνης</w>, but also occurring in Attic texts (LSJ). Cf. T27.2, ἐν τάχει. As this also concerns eyes (see line 2), this is probably a healing inscription. It is conceivable that <w lemma="εὔχομαι">εὐξάμενος</w> (or <w lemma="εὔχομαι">εὐξαμένη?</w>) follows: “As soon as I prayed…”<lb/>
                    3. Whether <w lemma="ἀλλά">ἀλλά</w> or <w lemma="ἄλλος">ἄλλα</w> is not clear. Then probably a form of <w lemma="λέγω">λέγω</w>.</ab>
            </div> 
